# Packet Tracer Labs
## Objective
This repository documents my practical networking journey using Packet Tracer.
My goal is not only to complete labs, but also to understand how networks work internally, troubleshoot problems, and build a strong foundation for enterprise networking.
## Learning Goals
- Strengthen networking concepts beyond CCNA memorization
- Build and troubleshoot real lab scenarios
- Practice structured documentation
- Analyze how protocols behave
- Progress toward designing enterprise-level networks
## Lab Roadmap
This lab sequence is inspired by the practical CCNA roadmap shared by GuruTech Networking and adapted to fit my own learning goals and study process.
The purpose is not simply completing labs, but understanding concepts deeply and building practical networking skills.
